TntL.jpg&h=ccbb7478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n突然間話12月份佣要分6份，呢樣你又唔預先講，即係如果9千蚊佣分俾我同&quot;熊貓&quot;兩份有$4500，而家咪變左每人$1500？咁打去&quot;江青&quot;度問啦，佢竟然又唔知12月係咁樣計佣喎，咁即係你無諗住分俾佢地啦，咁其實係咪諗住明明要出9千，而家你就攞3千佣出來就算呢？你唔係諗住咁L樣呃9我地呀？DLLM，你間濕鳩美容黑店對住啲員工真係好似對住啲客人咁劏客咁劏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f295483cb77c3e684e6e9bb447a76353774c829","tid":979027,"uid":229995,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:36:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LNH8VS1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLNH8VS1.jpg&h=6bedfc17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Oq20jH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Oq20jH.jpg&h=5eec24ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQLRTEH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQLRTEH.jpg&h=387b945d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nON撚79！有邊個香港人出來打工唔係為左份糧而做架，我同你有親都要出糧架，你分少左錢俾我又要我做野緊係唔得啦，我做乜L野要為你公司著想呀，有時真係唔L明啲支那人個閪腦諗啲咩，你活喺你個世界都無理由要逼所有人跟隨住你個世界嘅方式生活架，基本上我喺呢間公司做左半年，所經歷嘅野正正就反映出今時今日香港人係點樣俾呢個閪國嘅人折磨到咩地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b01d039e30a1a0ca7dea2e78d3697eafa64a65c7","tid":979027,"uid":16567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:40:49.000Z","msg":"做美容雞仲要幫支那蝗？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a1e5640205ce822d33f19f6d2db140c89bc5a1","tid":979027,"uid":229995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T11:52:08.000Z","msg":"我唔駛走呀，而家返到去打完卡乜都唔駛做又有糧出，間舖無客上來又唔會關我事"},{"pid":"d6eecd8d433d9d6360596e22a4e258d24c1d1146","tid":979027,"uid":53660,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-12T13:25:00.000Z","msg"